# Fuzzy Name Matching System

A comprehensive implementation of fuzzy name matching techniques to handle various name obstacles including phonetic similarities, transliterations, nicknames, and cultural variations.

## Overview

This project implements the complete internship curriculum on "Noun Obstacles and Phonetics" covering five major fuzzy matching techniques and their practical applications.

