## Performance Characteristics

| Method | Time Complexity | Space Complexity | Best For |
|--------|----------------|------------------|----------|
| Soundex | O(n) | O(1) | Quick phonetic grouping |
| Levenshtein | O(mn) | O(mn) | General string matching |
| Damerau | O(mn) | O(mn) | Typo correction |
| Jaro-Winkler | O(mn) | O(m+n) | Short strings, prefixes |
| Two-Pass Hybrid | O(k·m) | O(n) | Large databases |

Where: n, m = string lengths, k = candidates in phonetic group

## Challenges Handled

- ✅ Phonetic similarity (sound-alikes)
